# East and North Hertfordshire – Type 2 Together groups
Listed below are the Type 2 Together groups that are currently up and running
in the Eastern and North Hertfordshire area. Please note that meeting dates
are subject to change so please email the Eastern regional team if you'd like
to join a group - eastern@diabetes.org.uk (or update your listing).
