St Andrews Church Hall (Back of Church), St Andrews Street, Hertford. Last
Thursday of every month at 7.00pm. Contact: Pam Gates pam.gates@lineone.net
Waitrose, The Lairage, Hitchin SG5 1HF. First Tuesday each month at 10.30pm.
